  <brief_title>More Intensive Cardiac Rehabilitation Programs in Less Time</brief_title>
  <acronym>másPORmenos</acronym>
  <official_title>Multicenter, Prospective, Randomized, Open, Blinded for the End Point Evaluator to Compare Compliance to Secondary Prevention Measures After Acute Coronary Syndrome and Intensive Cardiac Rehabilitation Program vs Standard Program</official_title>
